snippet.title: Piff the Magic Dragon
snippet.description: Piff the Magic Dragon is the Las Vegas headlining sensation best known for his hilarious appearances on America’s Got Talent and Penn & Teller Fool Us. See him and Mr. Piffles LIVE in the Flamingo Showroom at the Flamingo Hotel and Casino or on tour in a city near you.
